192
00:07:41,960 --> 00:07:45,320
Frame of reference, simply for our purposes here,

193
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:51,580
means a state of motion of a set of coordinates.

194
00:07:51,580 --> 00:07:52,280
If you like, the way

195
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:52,980
to think about it is to,

196
00:07:52,980 --> 00:07:57,380
