206
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:34,220
God's time was the same for everybody.

207
00:08:34,220 --> 00:08:36,659
There was no question of what the time was

208
00:08:36,659 --> 00:08:38,080
on a particular clock.

209
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:40,059
Clocks were synchronized.

210
00:08:40,059 --> 00:08:41,580
It didn't matter how they moved.

211
00:08:41,580 --> 00:08:43,419
It didn't matter how you move.

212
00:08:43,419 --> 00:08:45,560
It didn't matter how you move with your watch

213
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:47,280
or without your watch.

214
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:51,720
Everybody would agree at every instant, at every place,

215
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:55,960
in the world, on what the time is, T.

216
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:59,360
That, of course, had to be given up

217
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:03,200
