248
00:10:17,020 --> 00:10:19,100
You have to have a good sense of gravity.

249
00:10:19,100 --> 00:10:20,080
You have to have a good sense of alignment.

250
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:20,120
You have to have a good sense of alignment.

251
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:20,200
You have to have a good sense of alignment.

252
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:20,240
You have to have a good sense of alignment.

253
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:22,000
There's a lot of different aspects of physics.

254
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:25,220
Of course, you may not consciously be using those,

255
